   \"thinking\": \"All clean. Let me now provide a comprehensive summary of what was done.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"All clean. Here's a summary of everything that was done:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## ✅ Completed: Map remaining MAIY Tech Hub features\\n\\n### Frontend (`maiy-tech-hub` — pushed to `maiy develop`)\\n\\n**`lib/api.ts`** — Major rewrite:\\n- Fixed `ApiArticle` / `ApiArticleSummary` types to match actual Prisma backend shape (`id`, `author` as nested object, `coverImage` instead of `hero`, `publishedAt` as nullable)\\n- Fixed `ApiArticlesResponse` → `pagination: { page, limit, total, totalPages }` (backend format)\\n- Added `fetchAdminArticles()` — `GET /api/articles?published=all` with JWT auth\\n- Added `createArticle()`, `updateArticle()`, `deleteArticle()`, `togglePublish()`\\n- Added `uploadImage()`, `uploadVideo()` — multipart form-data to Cloudinary via backend\\n- Added `searchArticlesBackend()` — `GET /api/articles?search=X`\\n- Added `tag`, `search` params to `fetchArticles()`\\n\\n**`lib/content.ts`** — Added 3 new exports:\\n- `getAllTags()` — aggregates tag counts from all articles, sorted by frequency\\n- `searchArticles()` — calls backend search + client-side tag filter fallback\\n- `getAdminArticles()` — fetches all articles including unpublished for admin\\n\\n**`app/admin/articles/page.tsx`** — Full rewrite as `'use client'`:\\n- Fetches all articles via `fetchAdminArticles()` (requires JWT)\\n- Shows status filter: All / Đã đăng / Nháp\\n- Actions: Toggle publish (🜁 Globe icon), View, Edit, Delete\\n- Refresh button, article count stats\\n\\n**`app/admin/articles/new/page.tsx`** — Connected to backend:\\n- Calls `POST /api/articles` with JWT auth\\n- Image upload via `uploadImage()` → Cloudinary\\n- Category → backend enum mapping (`ctdl` → `CTDL`, etc.)\\n- Publish/draft toggle\\n\\n**`app/admin/articles/[id]/page.tsx`** — New file:\\n- Loads article via `fetchArticle(id)` \\n- Edit form with `PUT /api/articles/:id`\\n- Image upload via `uploadImage()`\\n- Toggle publish via `PATCH /api/articles/:id/publish`\\n- Preview link to public article\\n\\n**`app/tags/page.tsx`** — No code changes needed — already uses `getAllArticles()` which now reads from backend ✓\\n\\n**`app/search/page.tsx`** — No code changes needed — already uses `getAllArticles()` + Fuse.js for client-side search ✓\\n\\n### Backend (`maiy-tech-hub-be` — pushed to `origin main`)\\n\\n**`src/routes/articles.ts`** — Added `?published=all` support:\\n- `GET /api/articles?published=all` requires JWT + ADMIN role\\n- Returns all articles including unpublished (for admin dashboard)\\n- Fixed `totalPages` calculation bug (was using `query.length` instead of `total`)\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 65,\n            \"output\": 645,\n            \"totalTokens\": 49591,\n            \"cacheRead\": 48610,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 271,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776620709447,\n          \"responseId\": \"063447a6c010689fc88ec590c0dc900d\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"f69ecf28\",\n            \"seq\": 83\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:senior-backend:subagent:743b2620-4597-40c3-a201-35bbae80bde7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"label\": \"senior-backend-maiy\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-senior-backend-subagent-743b2620-4597-40c3-a201-35bbae80bde7\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegr