s (`ApiArticle`, `ApiArticleSummary`, `ApiComment`, `ApiUser`, etc.) and helper functions for articles, auth (login/register/logout), newsletter, comments, rooms, and JWT token management\\n- **`.gitignore`** — Added to prevent `node_modules`, `.next`, `.env` from being committed\\n\\n### Files modified:\\n- **`lib/content.ts`** — Completely rewritten to use `lib/api.ts` instead of filesystem MDX. Same public API (`getAllArticles`, `getArticleBySlug`, `getArticlesByCategory`, `getRecentArticles`, `getFeaturedArticles`, `getAllSlugs`) — no component changes needed\\n- **`components/shared/newsletter-form.tsx`** — Now calls `POST ${API_URL}/api/newsletter/subscribe` (plus wired up the name field to the API body)\\n- **`app/admin/login/page.tsx`** — Now calls `POST ${API_URL}/api/auth/login` with email+password, stores JWT in `localStorage`\\n- **`components/admin/logout-btn.tsx`** — Calls backend logout endpoint + clears local tokens\\n\\n### TypeScript: ✅ Passes `tsc --noEmit` with zero errors\\n\\n### Known pre-existing issue:\\nThe `next build` fails at \\\"PageNotFoundError: Cannot find module for page: /api/admin/articles\\\" — this is a **pre-existing issue** unrelated to these changes (the route handler file exists but Next.js can't resolve it at build time). Fixing this is out of scope for this task.\\n\\n### To push:\\nThe local commit `3cdbe5d` on `develop` branch is ready. Run `git push origin develop` when GitLab credentials are available.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 100,\n            \"output\": 488,\n            \"totalTokens\": 51574,\n            \"cacheRead\": 50617,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 369,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776619370122,\n          \"respo