title, excerpt, content, category, tags, authorId, readingTime, published, publishedAt\\n- `Comment.ts` — articleId, authorId (nullable), authorName, content, parentId (nullable)\\n- `Newsletter.ts` — email, subscribed, subscribedAt, unsubscribedAt\\n- `StudyRoom.ts` — code, name, creatorId, isActive, expiresAt\\n- `RefreshToken.ts` — token, userId, expiresAt\\n\\n**2. MongoDB plugin** (`src/plugins/mongodb.ts`) — Mongoose connection with Fastify\\n\\n**3. All routes migrated** — `auth`, `articles`, `comments`, `newsletter`, `rooms`, `users` now use Mongoose models\\n\\n**4. Config updated** — `DATABASE_URL` → `MONGODB_URL`\\n\\n**5. docker-compose.yml** — PostgreSQL → MongoDB (mongo:7)\\n\\n**6. Seed script** — Prisma → Mongoose (admin: `admin@maiy.tech` / `maiy2026`)\\n\\n**7. API.md** — Full API documentation with all endpoints, request/response examples, auth flow\\n\\n**8. scripts/deploy.sh** — VPS deployment script\\n\\n**9. Dockerfile** — Updated for MongoDB\\n\\n### Build: ✅ Clean TypeScript compile\\n### Pushed: ✅ GitLab `main` branch\\n\\n### Key changes preserved:\\n- API endpoints identical to before\\n- JWT auth logic unchanged\\n- Cloudinary upload routes unchanged\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 86,\n            \"output\": 407,\n            \"totalTokens\": 55406,\n            \"cacheRead\": 54675,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 238,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776618295287,\n          \"responseId\": \"06343e3857e33375480794fa32d4f6c7\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"bce259ee\",\n            \"seq\": 169\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:1f14e5c6-7924-439c-ac7c-9d66f9e718fc\",\n    