 scroll — pure `requestAnimationFrame` with ease-out cubic, staggered 150ms per stat, no heavy libraries\\n\\n**✅ Issue 3 — Performant background effects**: Replaced the static blur orb with 5 CSS-only floating gradient orbs (`@keyframes floatOrb1/2/3`) using keyframe animations. No JS, no Framer Motion, no heavy blur — just CSS `transform` + `filter: blur()`. Orbs use `position: absolute` with `borderRadius: 50%` and low opacity (0.07–0.12). Smooth, lightweight, zero lag.\\n\\n**Bonus fix**: Resolved 2 pre-existing TypeScript errors in `career-roadmap.tsx` — added `summary?: string` and `salary?: string` to `SkillNode` interface, plus a null-coalescing fallback for `node.salary.split()`.\\n\\n**Build**: ✅ Compiled successfully, 47 static pages generated.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 181,\n            \"output\": 373,\n            \"totalTokens\": 39380,\n            \"cacheRead\": 37612,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 1214,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776603281518,\n          \"responseId\": \"06340392c14438df59de8ae71dc2b748\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a6d03500\",\n            \"seq\": 43\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:8b096a82-5e94-42ba-9a87-ce459a101621\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"label\": \"maiy-roadmap-v2\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-ui-ux-pro-max-subagent-8b096a82-5e94-42ba-9a87-ce459a101621\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram