nt:d14c2d24-4196-4dda-918a-117cfc16431b","agent:senior-backend:subagent:93f14721-a359-49c9-b181-b3f6ad0e0905","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:d189bc97-8ccb-4e51-8a7f-9e583b64092f","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:7ab66be8-3f9f-4c3d-930d-c88514a51549"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/0aac4c12-063e-4c35-8905-a6ea419eba0e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bây giờ làm sao để tôi khởi tạo một session mới bạn"}],"timestamp":1776621654376,"__openclaw":{"id":"63859372","seq":4108},"senderLabel":"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know how to start a new session with me. They want to know how to reset or start fresh. Let me explain their options."},{"type":"text","text":"Có 2 cách:\n\n**Cách 1 — Nói chuyện với tôi ở đây (Telegram)**\nTin nhắn này chính là session mới rồi đó — tôi vẫn nhớ mọi thứ từ memory files, chỉ context window hiện tại bị giới hạn thôi.\n\n**Cách 2 — Xóa session history để bắt đầu sạch**\nTôi sẽ xóa conversation history của session này:\n\n/purge\n\n**Cách 3 — Reset memory hoàn toàn**\nMuốn tôi quên hết mọi thứ và bắt đầu lại từ đầu không?\n\n---\n\nBạn muốn làm gì? Dùng cách nào cũng được — tôi vẫn nhớ tất cả qua memory files (không mất)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":103,"output":268,"totalTokens":109995,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":109624,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776621654396,"responseId":"06344b58af0cb0535fcb2ed8de48f1e6","__openclaw":{"id":"639d0659","seq":4109}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776621377905,"sessionId":"267be008-a295-4e44-aab6-59f510cf7591","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":40206,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776621370921,"endedAt":1776621377607,"runtimeMs":6686,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:52f0c795-a0e6-4fbc-9372-fe4cf966a590","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:29c204b1-bb3d-4d10-b20f-c9f805210680"],"thinkingLevel":"high","systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/267be008-a295-4e44-aab6-59f510cf7591.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, April 19th, 2026 - 5:56 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-19 17:56 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776621370920,"__openclaw":{"id":"89838bc4","seq":1654}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"~30 min after last check. Nothing new."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":82,"output":19,"totalTokens":40225,"cacheRead":6966,"cacheWrite":33158,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776621370932,"responseId":"06344a3c9521a570d0ec4e13478fafa7","__openclaw":{"id":"317845e0","seq":1655}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:7ab66be8-3f9f-4c3d-930d-c88514a51549","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"frontend-backend-map-2","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-7ab66be8-3f9f-4c3d-930d-c88514a51549","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776621236635,"sessionId":"4615c60b-2030-481c-8549-462a991c1bf4","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":48946,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776620319021,"endedAt":1776620720762,"runtimeMs":343388,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/4615c60b-2030-481c-8549-462a991c1bf4.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All clean. Let me now provide a comprehensive summary of what was done."},{"type":"text","text":"All clean. Here's a summary of everything that was done:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Completed: Map remaining MAIY Tech Hub features\n\n### Frontend (`maiy-tech-hub` — pushed to `maiy develop`)\n\n**`lib/api.ts`** — Major rewrite:\n- Fixed `ApiArticle` / `ApiArticleSummary` types to match actual Prisma backend shape (`id`, `author` as nested object, `coverImage` instead of `hero`, `publishedAt` as nullable)\n- Fixed `ApiArticlesResponse` → `pagination: { page, limit, total, totalPages }` (backend format)\n- Added `fetchAdminArticles()` — `GET /api/articles?published=all` with JWT auth\n- Added `createArticle()`, `updateArticle()`, `deleteArticle()`, `togglePublish()`\n- Added `uploadImage()`, `uploadVideo()` — multipart form-data to Cloudinary via backend\n- Added `searchArticlesBackend()` — `GET /api/articles?search=X`\n- Added `tag`, `search` params to `fetchArticles()`\n\n**`lib/content.ts`** — Added 3 new exports:\n- `getAllTags()` — aggregates tag counts from all articles, sorted by frequency\n- `searchArticles()` — calls backend search + client-side tag filter fallback\n- `getAdminArticles()` — fetches all articles including unpublished for admin\n\n**`app/admin/articles/page.tsx`** — Full rewrite as `'use client'`:\n- Fetches all articles via `fetchAdminArticles()` (requires JWT)\n- Shows status filter: All / Đã đăng / Nháp\n- Actions: Toggle publish (🜁 Globe icon), View, Edit, Delete\n- Refresh button, article count stats\n\n**`app/admin/articles/new/page.tsx`** — Connected to backend:\n- Calls `POST /api/articles` with JWT auth\n- Image upload via `uploadImage()` → Cloudinary\n- Category → backend enum mapping (`ctdl` → `CTDL`, etc.)\n- Publish/draft toggle\n\n**`app/admin/articles/[id]/page.tsx`** — New file:\n- Loads article via `fetchArticle(id)` \n- Edit form with `PUT /api/articles/:id`\n- Image upload via `uploadImage()`\n- Toggle publish via `PATCH /api/articles/:id/publish`\n- Preview link to public article\n\n**`app/tags/page.tsx`** — No code changes needed — already uses `getAllArticles()` which now reads from backend ✓\n\n**`app/search/page.tsx`** — No code changes needed — already uses `getAllArticles()` + Fuse.js for client-side search ✓\n\n### Backend (`maiy-tech-hub-be` — pushed to `origin main`)\n\n**`src/routes/articles.ts`** — Added `?published=all` support:\n- `GET /api/articles?published=all` requires JWT + ADMIN role\n- Returns all articles including unpublished (for admin dashboard)\n- Fixed `totalPages` calculation bug (was using `query.length` instead of `total`)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":65,"output":645,"totalTokens":49591,"cacheRead":48610,"cacheWrite":271,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776620709447,"responseId":"063447a6c010689fc88ec590c0dc900d","__openclaw":{"id":"f69ecf28","seq":83}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:743b2620-4597-40c3-a201-35bbae80bde7","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"senior-backend-maiy","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-senior-backend-subagent-743b2620-4597-40c3-a201-35bbae80bde7","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776621164429,"sessionId":"2ad28a7f-a811-4d