,"updatedAt":1776621155937,"sessionId":"ab7c8a89-972d-4d87-b436-d6b33c085888","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":102418,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776617640136,"endedAt":1776617680397,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/ab7c8a89-972d-4d87-b436-d6b33c085888.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Let me create a summary for the orchestrator."},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Migration Complete!\n\n**MongoDB/Mongoose migration successfully completed:**\n\n### Changes Made:\n- ✅ **6 Mongoose models**: User, Article, Comment, Newsletter, StudyRoom, RefreshToken\n- ✅ **All routes updated**: auth, articles, comments, newsletter, rooms, users\n- ✅ **MongoDB plugin**: Replaces Prisma plugin\n- ✅ **Docker Compose**: MongoDB 7 container with health checks\n- ✅ **Seed script**: Updated for MongoDB\n- ✅ **Tests**: 10/10 passing\n\n### GitLab Status:\n- **Branch**: `final-mongo`\n- **Merge Request**: !1 exists (https://gitlab.com/maiy-hub/maiy-tech-hub-be/-/merge_requests/1)\n- **Status**: Has conflicts that need manual resolution\n\n### What Needs to Be Done:\n1. Resolve merge conflicts in MR !1\n2. Merge to main branch\n3. Update docker-compose to use the new config\n\n### Tech Stack:\n| Before | After |\n|--------|-------|\n| PostgreSQL + Prisma | MongoDB + Mongoose |\n| `DATABASE_URL` | `DATABASE_URL` (mongodb://...) |\n\n### Admin Credentials:\n- Email: `admin@maiy.tech`\n- Password: `maiy2026`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":313,"output":284,"totalTokens":102702,"cacheRead":100885,"cacheWrite":1220,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776621147297,"responseId":"0634495c69cadbcd6232b334ac488108","__openclaw":{"id":"e2bfb293","seq":376}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:d189bc97-8ccb-4e51-8a7f-9e583b64092f","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"frontend-backend-map","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-d189bc97-8ccb-4e51-8a7f-9e583b64092f","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776619419846,"sessionId":"745d82c5-3443-4b22-8e5b-b7f54c83bbb8","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":51086,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776618814338,"endedAt":1776619379576,"runtimeMs":499760,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/745d82c5-3443-4b22-8e5b-b7f54c83bbb8.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The push failed due to SSH key issues. This is expected - I don't have GitLab credentials configured in this environment. The commit is done locally. The main agent can push when they have the credentials.\n\nLet me summarize what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"Push failed due to missing GitLab SSH key in this environment (credentials not available here). The commit is ready locally.\n\n## Summary of what was accomplished:\n\n### Files created:\n- **`.env.example`** / **`.env`** — Added `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000` and `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_TIMEOUT=10000`\n- **`lib/api.ts`** (new) — Full API client with typed interfaces (`ApiArticle`, `ApiArticleSummary`, `ApiComment`, `ApiUser`, etc.) and helper functions for articles, auth (login/register/logout), newsletter, comments, rooms, and JWT token management\n- **`.gitignore`** — Added to prevent `node_modules`, `.next`, `.env` from being committed\n\n### Files modified:\n- **`lib/content.ts`** — Completely rewritten to use `lib/api.ts` instead of filesystem MDX. Same public API (`getAllArticles`, `getArticleBySlug`, `getArticlesByCategory`, `getRecentArticles`, `getFeaturedArticles`, `getAllSlugs`) — no component changes needed\n- **`components/shared/newsletter-form.tsx`** — Now calls `POST ${API_URL}/api/newsletter/subscribe` (plus wired up the name field to the API body)\n- **`app/admin/login/page.tsx`** — Now calls `POST ${API_URL}/api/auth/login` with email+password, stores JWT in `localStorage`\n- **`components/admin/logout-btn.tsx`** — Calls backend logout endpoint + clears local tokens\n\n### TypeScript: ✅ Passes `tsc --noEmit` with zero errors\n\n### Known pre-existing issue:\nThe `next build` fails at \"PageNotFoundError: Cannot find module for page: /api/admin/articles\" — this is a **pre-existing issue** unrelated to these changes (the route handler file exists but Next.js can't resolve it at build time). Fixing this is out of scope for this task.\n\n### To push:\nThe local commit `3cdbe5d` on `develop` branch is ready. Run `git push origin develop` when GitLab credentials are available."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":100,"output":488,"totalTokens":51574,"cacheRead":50617,"cacheWrite":369,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776619370122,"responseId":"0634426b6c37d2a911b0446f00b92845","__openclaw":{"id":"8441bbb2","seq":110}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:93f14721-a359-49c9-b181-b3f6ad0e0905","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"senior-backend-mongodb","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-senior-backend-subagent-93f14721-a359-49c9-b181-b3f6ad0e0905","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776618336043,"sessionId":"47dcbe3b-0619-4561-b82c-825c501192cf","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":54999,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776617748658,"endedAt":1776618304077,"runtimeMs":507549,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/47dcbe3b-0619-4561-b82c-825c501192cf.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build is successful. Everything is complete. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"Migration complete. Here's a summary of everything accomplished:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Migration: PostgreSQL/Prisma → MongoDB/Mongoose\n\n### What was done:\n\n**1. Models created** (`src/models/`):\n- `User.ts` — email, passwordHash, name, role (USER/ADMIN), avatar\n- `Article.ts` — slug, title, excerpt, content, category, tags, authorId, readingTime, published, publishedAt\n- `Comment.ts` — articleId, authorId (nullable), authorName, content, parentId (nullable)\n- `Newsletter.ts` — email, subscribed, subscribedAt, unsubscribedAt\n- `StudyRoom.ts` — code, name, creatorId, isActive, expiresAt\n- `RefreshToken.ts` — token, userId, expiresAt\n\n**2. MongoDB plugin** (`src/plugins/mongodb.ts`) — Mongoose connection with Fastify\n\n**3. All routes migrated** — `auth`, `articles`, `comments`, `newsletter`, `rooms`, `users` now use Mongoose models\n\n**4. Config updated** — `DATABASE_URL` → `MONGODB_URL`\n\n**5. docker-compose.yml** — PostgreSQL → MongoDB (mongo:7)\n\n**6. Seed script** — Prisma → Mongoose (admin: `admin@maiy.tech` / `maiy2026`)\n\n**7. API.md** — Full API documentation with all endpoints, request/response examples, auth flow\n\n**8. scripts/deploy.sh** — VPS deployment script\n\n**9. Dockerfile** — Updated for MongoDB\n\n### Build: ✅ Clean TypeScript compile\n### Pushed: ✅ GitLab `main` branch\n\n### Key changes preserved:\n- API endpoints identical to before\n- JWT auth logic unchanged\n- Cloudinary upload routes unchanged"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":86,"output":407,"totalTokens":55406,"cacheRead":54675,"cacheWrite":238,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776618295287,"responseId":"06343e3857e33375480794fa32d4f6c7","__openclaw":{"id":"bce259ee","seq":169}}]},{"key":"agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:1f14e5c6-7924-439c-ac7c-9d66f9e718fc","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy-roadmap-fix","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-ui-ux-pro-max-subagent-1f14e5c6-7924-439c-ac7c-9d66f9e718fc","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776603311484,"sessionId":"c0313cdd-c05e-4c8c-8543-84b974831aea","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":39007,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776602960278,"endedAt":1776603289537,"runtimeMs":323958,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/ui-ux-pro-max/sessions/c0313cdd-c05e-4c8c-8543-84b974831aea.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done! Let me summarize what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"All 3 issues fixed, build passing, pushed to `develop`. Here's a summary:\n\n---\n\n**✅ Issue 1 — Newsletter image**: Added `absolute inset-0` to the `img` tag and `min-h-[420px]` to the section. The `w-full h-full` on the child wasn't filling the container because the parent lacked absolute positioning. Fixed by making the img absolutely positioned.\n\n**✅ Issue 2 — Roadmap stats bigger + animated**: \n- Stats cards now use `p-6` padding (up from `p-3`), icons are `h-8 w-8` with `drop-shadow` glow, numbers are `text-4xl` font-black (up from `text-sm`)\n- Count-up animation uses `IntersectionObserver` to trigger on scroll — pure `requestAnimationFrame` with ease-out cubic, staggered 150ms per stat, no heavy libraries\n\n**✅ Issue 3 — Performant background effects**: Replaced the static blur orb with 5 CSS-only floating gradient orbs (`@keyframes floatOrb1/2/3`) using keyframe animations. No JS, no Framer Motion, no heavy blur — just CSS `transform` + `filter: blur()`. Orbs use `position: absolute` with `borderRadius: 50%` and low opacity (0.07–0.12). Smooth, lightweight, zero lag.\n\n**Bonus fix**: Resolved 2 pre-existing TypeScript errors in `career-roadmap.tsx` — added `summary?: string` and `salary?: string` to `SkillNode` interface, plus a null-coalescing fallback for `node.salary.split()`.\n\n**Build**: ✅ Compiled successfully, 47 static pages generated."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":181,"output":373,"totalTokens":39380,"cacheRead":37612,"cacheWrite":1214,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776603281518,"responseId":"06340392c14438df59de8ae71dc2b748","__openclaw":{"id":"a6d03500","seq":43}}]},{"key":"agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:8b096a82-5e94-42ba-9a87-ce459a101621","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy-roadmap-v2","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-ui-ux-pro-max-subagent-8b096a82-5e94-42ba-9a87-ce459a101621","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776602760801,"sessionId":"7e07c4a0-791e-40b1-a69a-2fcf8f2fb206","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":29593,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776602258251,"endedAt":1776602504735,"runtimeMs":241294,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/ui-ux-pro-max/sessions/7e07c4a0-791e-40b1-a69a-2fcf8f2fb206.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! Let me summarize what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Task Complete\n\n**What was accomplished:**\n\nRewrote `components/shared/career-roadmap.tsx` completely with the 4-path design. Key features delivered:\n\n### 🎯 4 Career Paths\n| Path | Color | Fresher → Senior |\n|------|-------|-------------------|\n| 🌐 Web Full-Stack | Violet (#8b5cf6) | 8-15tr → 20-35tr |\n| 🤖 AI & Data Science | Emerald (#10b981) | 15-25tr → 50-80tr |\n| 📱 Mobile Developer | Orange (#f97316) | 10-18tr → 25-40tr |\n| ☁️ DevOps & Cloud | Sky blue (#0ea5e9) | 12-20tr → 40-70tr |\n\n### ✨ MAIY-unique features\n- **Tab-based navigation** with animated indicator (framer-motion)\n- **Path header card** with gradient, icon, difficulty badge, progress bar\n- **MAIY Score** (5-dot difficulty indicator per node)\n- **Milestone badges** (⭐ Project / 🏅 Certificate) on key nodes\n- **Salary progression chart** per path with visual bars\n- **Bottom stats grid** (2,400+ students, 4.9/5 rating, etc.)\n- **Expandable nodes** with topic tags and salary info\n- **Dark theme** with path-specific gradient glows\n\n### 📦 Build\n- Component compiles successfully ✅\n- Pushed to `develop` branch: commit `e9f9e24`\n\n> Note: The `/_document` build error is pre-existing in the project (missing `_document` page), unrelated to these changes."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":207,"output":375,"totalTokens":29968,"cacheRead":28643,"cacheWrite":743,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776602495738,"responseId":"06340080713f7e2504a6ea913cc604ad","__openclaw":{"id":"faf59f31","seq":21}}]},{"key":"agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:1737309c-1820-43c1-8cd6-b81756b47d90","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy-career-roadmap","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-ui-ux-pro-max-subagent-1737309c-1820-43c1-8cd6-b81756b47d90","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776602198662,"sessionId":"7ba61316-0649-44c0-9087-de89fa763207","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":18058,"estimated