pe":"thinking","thinking":"The push was successful. Let me now provide a comprehensive summary of what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"All changes pushed successfully. Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ SEO Audit & Optimization Complete\n\n**Commit:** `6983d7a` — pushed to `maiy/feat/redesign`\n\n### What was found & fixed:\n\n| Area | Issue | Fix |\n|---|---|---|\n| **`layout.tsx`** | Missing `theme-color`, global og:image, twitter:image, icons, GoogleBot rules | Complete metadata overhaul |\n| **`articles/[slug]`** | `BreadcrumbSchema` imported but **never rendered**; missing canonical, twitter | Fixed rendering + full OG/Twitter |\n| **`category/[slug]`** | Same BreadcrumbSchema bug; missing canonical, twitter | Fixed rendering + full OG/Twitter |\n| **`article-schema.tsx`** | No `keywords`, `dateModified`, `articleSection` | Added all fields |\n| **`breadcrumb-schema.tsx`** | `href` was required — broke on current-page items | Made optional |\n| **Music/Study pages** | No metadata (client components) | New `layout.tsx` files with full metadata |\n| **All 12+ pages** | No canonical URLs, incomplete OG/Twitter | Canonical + OG + Twitter cards added |\n\n### Pages with complete SEO metadata now:\n`layout`, `articles/[slug]`, `articles/category/[slug]`, `articles`, `about`, `contact`, `premium/layout`, `music/layout`, `study/layout`, `search`, `tags`, `changelog`, `privacy`, `terms`\n\n### Build result: **45/45 pages** ✅  \n*(Pre-existing `/admin/articles` error is unrelated to these changes — confirmed by git stash test)*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":163,"output":362,"totalTokens":69062,"cacheRead":68184,"cacheWrite":353,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776599052077,"responseId":"0633f30eb6e36a60b0de1029401a9d40","__openclaw":{"id":"57ca6300","seq":119}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:4bbd5306-6368-44ab-8122-d38c4c851497","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy-tags-frontend","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-4bbd5306-6368-44ab-8122-d38c4c851497","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776597428847,"sessionId":"f8225c5b-8a5d-4947-bb42-1d85d2dcf85b","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":22808,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776597191564,"endedAt":1776597393590,"runtimeMs":135940,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/f8225c5b-8a5d-4947-bb42-1d85d2dcf85b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Successfully committed and pushed. Let me summarize what was done."},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's a summary of what was fixed:\n\n## ✅ Tags Page Redesign Complete\n\n**Changes made to `app/tags/page.tsx`:**\n\n1. **Performance fix** — Removed `SectionParticles` entirely (was 30 canvas-animated bubbles + `requestAnimationFrame` loop = CPU drain, especially on mobile). No particles at all now.\n\n2. **Clean background** — Replaced messy 4-orb nebula with just 2 faint, subtle gradient blurs (`violet-600/[0.04]` and `blue-600/[0.03]`) plus the base `#09090b` background. Much more Apple/Linear-like.\n\n3. **Better visual hierarchy** — Added section divider bars (small gradient vertical lines + uppercase labels) between the Tag Cloud and Popular Tags sections. Clearer rhythm and flow.\n\n4. **Consistent with other pages** — Adopted the same pattern as `about`, `contact`, `music`: subtle gradient section dividers, clean card grid, no flashy decorations.\n\n5. **Kept everything that works** — Gradient text headings, colored tag icons, pill badges with counts, hover lift animations, dark theme colors.\n\n**Build:** 42/42 pages generated. The only error (`/admin/articles/page`) is pre-existing and unrelated to this change.\n\n**Git:** Committed and pushed to `maiy/feat/redesign` ✅"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":200,"output":305,"totalTokens":23113,"cacheRead":22375,"cacheWrite":233,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776597385857,"responseId":"0633ec8a8346efa06fe7a3ccd7b7b370","__openclaw":{"id":"05be18a9","seq":26}}]},{"key":"agent:playwright-pro:subagent:dd0659ed-4c5b-4f32-a2f1-99019f97b8cc","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy:playwright-pro","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-playwright-pro-subagent-dd0659ed-4c5b-4f32-a2f1-99019f97b8cc","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776574232315,"sessionId":"da7caf4a-2484-422a-9c90-973a4c328aa9","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":26366,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776573471013,"endedAt":1776573716299,"runtimeMs":136923,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/playwright-pro/sessions/da7caf4a-2484-422a-9c90-973a4c328aa9.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Chromium and FFmpeg installed. Let me summarize what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ E2E Test Setup Complete — MAIY Tech Hub\n\n### Files Created\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `tests/e2e/home.spec.ts` | Home page tests: title, hero section, nav links, dark mode toggle |\n| `tests/e2e/articles.spec.ts` | Articles: listing, detail page, category filter |\n| `tests/e2e/music.spec.ts` | Music page: loads, mood selector interaction |\n| `tests/e2e/study.spec.ts` | Study page: loads, create room button |\n| `tests/e2e/search.spec.ts` | Search: page loads, input interaction |\n| `tests/e2e/seo.spec.ts` | SEO: sitemap.xml, robots.txt, OG tags |\n| `playwright.config.ts` | Config: baseURL `localhost:3000`, webServer auto-starts `yarn dev`, HTML reporter, trace on retry |\n\n### Packages Installed\n- `@playwright/test@1.59.1` (with `playwright@1.59.1` + `playwright-core@1.59.1`)\n- Chromium 147 browser + FFmpeg (system deps installed via `--with-deps`)\n\n### To Run Tests\n```bash\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub\nnpx playwright test\n```\n\nTests auto-start the dev server (`yarn dev`) on port 3000 if not already running. HTML report generated at `playwright-report/index.html`."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":11218,"output":354,"totalTokens":26720,"cacheRead":14931,"cacheWrite":217,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776573708379,"responseId":"0633900dad73c264e799da3c4865611c","__openclaw":{"id":"7cea52ad","seq":22}}]},{"key":"agent:seo-audit:subagent:3fa1ad2c-5a53-4fee-b7b2-1434bfb54905","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy:seo-audit","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-seo-audit-subagent-3fa1ad2c-5a53-4fee-b7b2-1434bfb54905","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776574115040,"sessionId":"b89a4494-a880-4f58-904c-cbf71bed7c5b","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":16927,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776573471765,"endedAt":1776573599369,"runtimeMs":59350,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/seo-audit/sessions/b89a4494-a880-4f58-904c-cbf71bed7c5b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No TypeScript errors. All files created successfully."},{"type":"text","text":"✅ All files created, TS clean. Summary:\n\n**Completed (6/6):**\n\n1. **`app/api/revalidate/route.ts`** — On-demand ISR endpoint. Accepts `?secret=&path=` query params. Validates secret, then calls `revalidatePath` for a specific path or `revalidateTag('articles')` for all articles. Returns 401 on bad secret.\n\n2. **`components/seo/web-site-schema.tsx`** — Renders `WebSite` JSON-LD schema with SearchAction, publisher info, pulled from `config/site.ts`.\n\n3. **`components/seo/breadcrumb-schema.tsx`** — Renders `BreadcrumbList` JSON-LD. Hardcodes \"Trang chủ\" as item 1, then maps dynamic items starting at position 2.\n\n4. **`app/layout.tsx`** — Added `WebSiteSchema` import and placed `<WebSiteSchema />` just before `</body>` (inside ThemeProvider).\n\n5. **`app/about/page.tsx`** — New static about page with Vietnamese prose content, GitHub link, and heart emoji. Proper Next.js `Metadata` export for `<title>` and `<description>`.\n\n6. **`.env.example`** — Documents `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` and `REVALIDATE_SECRET` for deployers.\n\n**TypeScript: 0 errors.** All components use `@/config/site` which already exports `SITE`."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":60,"output":308,"totalTokens":17235,"cacheRead":16432,"cacheWrite":435,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776573591849,"responseId":"06338f98ec52fed97eb73e1a5e24abce","__openclaw":{"id":"350f9811","seq":22}}]},{"key":"agent:realistic-seeder:subagent:c428a233-d6ca-447c-94a5-ee2daac0dc5f","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"maiy:realistic-seeder","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-realistic-seeder-subagent-c428a233-d6ca-447c-94a5-ee2daac0dc5f","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776571673246,"sessionId":"f368d5f1-4ab1-463c-bf75-1b63ec01e74c","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextToken