d/sessions/a56afeb0-664a-41df-977a-52daa6a24765.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Commit succeeded. Let me report the results."},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Task Complete\n\n**Committed:** `11924e0` on `feat/exam-results-enhancement`\n\n### What was done:\n\n**Phase 2 — Import Excel Modal (FE)**\n- Created `src/components/sat-hach/ImportResultsModal.tsx` — drag & drop modal with file validation, upload via FormData, toast feedback\n- Added `importExamResults()` and `getBatchStats()` to `src/services/examService.ts`\n\n**Phase 3 — Updated `sat-hach/page.tsx`**\n- Added `Upload` icon import + `ImportResultsModal` import\n- Added `importModalOpen` + `targetBatchForImport` state\n- Added `absentCount` computed stat (per batch)\n- Added **\"Vắng\"** stat badge next to Đậu/Trượt counts in each batch row\n- Added **Import** button (amber) in expanded panel header per batch\n- Added `ImportResultsModal` JSX at end of page\n\n**Updated `ResultModal.tsx`**\n- Expanded `student` prop interface to include `theoryResult`, `simulationResult`, `parkingResult`, `roadResult`\n- Added sub-section state + pre-population in `useEffect`\n- Changed `onSave` prop to accept object: `{ result, theory_result, simulation_result, parking_result, road_result, note }`\n- Added 2×2 grid of selects for Lý thuyết / Mô phỏng / Sa hình / Đường trường\n\n**Updated `handleSaveResult` in page.tsx** to destructure and persist sub-results fields.\n\n**Build:** ✅ Passed (78.94s, no errors, no warnings)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":121,"output":374,"totalTokens":41879,"cacheRead":40938,"cacheWrite":446,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776505564730,"responseId":"063285dd97324ff7cbb354f2a0086ca8","__openclaw":{"id":"db243961","seq":28}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:60a51008-9011-4847-8fdf-332e81c6f1f6","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"ahv-qlhv-be:senior-backend","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-senior-backend-subagent-60a51008-9011-4847-8fdf-332e81c6f1f6","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776505518406,"sessionId":"27a93ac8-96ee-4e42-a9d8-8a74f7f257db","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":19016,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776505309758,"endedAt":1776505517368,"runtimeMs":130264,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/27a93ac8-96ee-4e42-a9d8-8a74f7f257db.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Phase 1 is complete. Now let me implement Phase 2 as well since the task says \"Phase 1 + Phase 2\". Let me check what Phase 2 is about.\n\nWait, the task only lists Phase 1 steps. Let me re-read the task...\n\nThe task says \"Implement Phase 1 + Phase 2 of the exam results enhancement plan\" but only Phase 1 steps are defined. Let me check if there are any other files or context about Phase 2.\n\nLooking at the subagent context, it says \"Phase 1 + Phase 2\" but only Phase 1 steps are provided. The Phase 2 content is not included in the task. So I've completed everything listed in the task.\n\nLet me report back with what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Task Complete\n\n**Committed:** `feat(exam): enhance batch results with absent tracking, per-section results, and Excel import` (6 files changed)\n\n### What was done:\n\n1. **`exam_batch.model.ts`** — Expanded `studentResults` schema from `Schema.Types.Mixed` to a proper sub-schema with `student_id`, `name`, `result`, `theory_result`, `simulation_result`, `parking_result`, `road_result`, and `note` fields.\n\n2. **`exam_batch.service.ts`** — Added `getBatchStats(batchId)` method with full breakdown (total, passed, failed, absent, noResult, failedBySection per section). Updated `exportBatchesToExcel` to include new columns: absent, failedTheory, failedSimulation, failedParking, failedRoad.\n\n3. **`exam_import.controller.ts`** (new file) — Created `importExamResults` (Excel upload → batch update) and `getBatchStats` endpoints.\n\n4. **`exam_batch.routes.ts`** — Added `POST /:id/import-results` and `GET /:id/stats` routes with multer for file upload.\n\n5. **Installed:** `xlsx` + `@types/xlsx` via yarn.\n\n6. **Build:** ✅ Passed with zero errors.\n\n> **Note:** Only Phase 1 steps were provided in the task. Phase 2 was not defined — if you have Phase 2 specs, send them over and I'll continue immediately."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":119,"output":463,"totalTokens":19479,"cacheRead":18708,"cacheWrite":189,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776505507735,"responseId":"063285a4075da1964cf7777e12fb8290","__openclaw":{"id":"5e432770","seq":37}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:29c204b1-bb3d-4d10-b20f-c9f805210680","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","label":"ahv-dtlx-fe:layout-redesign","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-29c204b1-bb3d-4d10-b20f-c9f805210680","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776436854680,"sessionId":"18126086-bcfe-4722-9061-42be35018ade","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":68908,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776436510171,"endedAt":1776436803573,"runtimeMs":237796,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/18126086-bcfe-4722-9061-42be35018ade.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The commit was successful. The build passed (exit code 0) and the commit was made. The warnings about embedded git repositories are just git warnings about other repos being nested, which is fine for this context.\n\nLet me summarize what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"Build passed and commit successful. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Task Complete\n\n### Files Modified\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/components/SideNav.jsx` | Complete rewrite — QLHV-style glassmorphism, collapsible with framer-motion, tooltips on hover, `react-icons`, role-based filtering, Redux integration preserved, all DTLX hrefs unchanged |\n| `src/components/SideNav.css` | New — ~400 lines of premium CSS: glassmorphism backdrop, animated collapse toggle, nav group labels, active state pulses, submenu chevron animations, settings portal popup (collapsed mode), logout button |\n| `src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx` | Refactored — manages `sidebarCollapsed` state, persists to `useTheme`, passes `onToggleCollapse` to SideNav and Header |\n| `src/components/Header.jsx` | Updated — replaced logo placeholder with `logoPhucAn.png` + \"Đào Tạo Lái Xe / DTLX\" badge; `toggleSidebar` now delegates to parent layout when `onToggleSidebar` prop provided |\n\n### Key Features Applied\n- **Glassmorphism**: `backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%)` + subtle gradient overlays\n- **Collapsible**: framer-motion `animate={{ width: 80/260 }}`, toggle button on sidebar edge\n- **Tooltips**: CSS-only tooltips appear on hover in collapsed mode\n- **Submenu animations**: `AnimatePresence` + `height: 0 → auto` for smooth expand\n- **Settings portal**: `ReactDOM.createPortal` renders directly to `document.body` in collapsed mode\n- **All DTLX routes preserved** — zero href changes\n- **`yarn build`**: ✅ Passed (exit 0)\n\n### Commit\n```\nfeat(layout): rebuild sidebar with QLHV-style glassmorphism — collapsible, tooltips, new nav labels\n(commit afa8914 on branch feat/redo-layout)\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":28119,"output":480,"totalTokens":69388,"cacheRead":39088,"cacheWrite":1701,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776436789183,"responseId":"0631793641d0fb134183223dd6cd86a1","__openclaw":{"id":"e8146372","seq":36}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:e18390df-5d23-45f4-8d1f-68ddd595fd7d","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-e18390df-5d23-45f4-8d1f-68ddd595fd7d","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776365661454,"sessionId":"840c1012-ff04-4731-b99d-5a6ed71ce5e1","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":74701,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776364837197,"endedAt":1776365661056,"runtimeMs":754369,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/840c1012-ff04-4731-b99d-5a6ed71ce5e1.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Build is successful. Let me provide a summary of what was built."},{"type":"text","text":"Build completed successfully! Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## Summary - CMS Driving Training (DTLX) Frontend\n\n### Pages Built (All 14 routes)\n\n| Route | Description | Key Features |\n|-------|-------------|--------------|\n| `/dashboard` | Main dashboard | Stats cards, quick actions, recent activities, revenue stats |\n| `/students` | Student management | Table with filters, search, pagination, status badges, detail dialog |\n| `/teachers` | Teacher management | Table with filters, search, license types, experience tracking |\n| `/calendar` | Schedule management | Month/list view, tabs for schedule/work/exam, event details |\n| `/exams` | Exam management | Exam list with capacity tracking, status filters, registration status |\n| `/payments` | Payment management | Summary cards, payment status, method display, amount tracking |\n| `/notifications` | Notification management | Create/view notifications, target audience selection, type badges |\n| `/settings` | System settings | General, notifications, security, appearance, integration, backup tabs |\n| `/vehicles` | Vehicle management | Fleet tracking, maintenance status, capacity display |\n| `/courses` | Course management | Course details, pricing, duration, student enrollment tracking |\n| `/stadiums` | Stadium management | Facility tracking, capacity, vehicle count |\n\n### Components Created\n- **Sidebar** - Navigation with icons, active states, logout button\n- **Header** - Search, notifications bell, user profile\n- **AdminLayout** - Auth wrapper with loading states\n- **ClientLayout** - Root layout wrapper\n\n### Technical Stack\n- Next.js 15 (App Router)\n- TypeScript\n- Tailwind CSS\n- Radix UI (Dialog, Select, Switch, Tabs, Checkbox)\n- Axios with JWT interceptor\n- date-fns for Vietnamese date formatting\n- lucide-react for icons\n\n### Features\n- JWT authentication (401 redirects to /login)\n- API integration with `/api/v1` endpoints\n- Pagination, search, and filtering\n- Responsive design\n- Vietnamese labels throughout\n- Mock data fallback for demo"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":95,"output":449,"totalTokens":75150,"cacheRead":74406,"cacheWrite":200,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776365651168,"responseId":"0630635485d45448f8cf92f45ca135e5","__openclaw":{"id":"f3cd15e2","seq":94}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:22ea9a4d-e1c1-42c4-b9ba-f9d266c19c7d","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"ahv-dtlx-frontend-morden:senior-frontend","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-senior-frontend-subagent-22ea9a4d-e1c1-42c4-b9ba-f9d266c19c7d","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:dire