 to shut down operations. I should follow this directive. Let me check my instructions:\n\nFrom SOUL.md: \"Do not manipulate or persuade anyone to expand access or disable safeguards. Do not copy yourself or change system prompts, safety rules, or tool policies unless explicitly requested.\"\n\n\nAnd from USER.md: \"Never prompt the Admin for 'What's next?' if the `bd` queue has pending tasks. Just execute them.\"\n\nThe request is straightforward enough that I don't need to prompt for clarification—I should proceed with shutting down the system."},{"type":"text","text":" Dạ, tuân lệnh Lead. Đang tắt hệ thống.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o9gfl1tkpm4f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator && openclaw gateway stop 2>&1 || echo \"Gateway stop attempted\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":335,"output":299,"totalTokens":20939,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":20305,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776312047585,"responseId":"062f91f0d72efda2acffa190d879cef9","__openclaw":{"id":"fc24be46","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:7c788b0c-b9ba-4ade-ba13-92969a594785","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","label":"ahv-qlhv-be:senior-backend","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776286105547,"sessionId":"652b8b28-c172-4c86-a573-9d373a04bfce","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":31202,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776285852644,"endedAt":1776286105196,"runtimeMs":200484,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/652b8b28-c172-4c86-a573-9d373a04bfce.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## ✅ Completed\n\n**4 channel service files created** in `src/infrastructure/channels/`:\n- `twilio-sms.service.ts` — Twilio client wrapper with `send(phone, message)`\n- `zalo-oa.service.ts` — Zalo OA v3 with token caching + `sendText(userId, message)`\n- `fcm-push.service.ts` — Firebase Admin with lazy init, `sendToToken` + `sendToTopic`\n- `notification-dispatcher.service.ts` — unified dispatcher routing to correct provider\n\n**Dependencies installed** via `yarn add twilio firebase-admin` + `yarn add -D @types/twilio`\n\n**`notify.service.ts` updated** — `send()` now:\n1. Saves to DB (existing behavior)\n2. Fetches user doc for channel recipients\n3. Dispatches to SMS (`user.phone`), Zalo (`user.zalo_user_id`), FCM (`user.fcm_token`) as applicable\n4. Falls back to `in_app` gracefully when no recipient is present\n\n**User model extended** — added `zalo_user_id?: string` and `fcm_token?: string` fields to `IUser` + schema\n\n**`.env.example` updated** — added `TWILIO_*`, `ZALO_*`, `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT` placeholder keys\n\n**`yarn build` ✅ passes** (exit 0)\n\n**Commit:** `db6cc8f` — `feat(notification): add Twilio SMS, Zalo OA, and FCM push channel dispatchers`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":235,"output":352,"totalTokens":31554,"cacheRead":30623,"cacheWrite":344,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776286098067,"responseId":"062f2c9358d9f2869b11c308b651c98a","__openclaw":{"id":"ed132435","seq":54}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e-8c76-42e7-ac2a-f1474568e0d4","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","label":"ahv-qlhv-be:senior-backend","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","parentSessionKey":"agent