{"type":"message","id":"7a3a702f","parentId":"5239d5b0","timestamp":"2026-04-20T00:55:41.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context. The current dashboard uses:\n- Ant Design (Card, Row, Col)- Redux for state management\n- Revenue, Expense, Profit, Debt cards\n- Charts (Student, Teacher, Revenue, Payment, Debt)\n\nThe new design needs:\n- Custom sidebar with logo\n- Dashboard with stat cards showing Giáo viên, Học viên with amounts\n- Calendar grid (max 6 visible, scrollable or list toggle)\n- Chi phí table with scrollbar\n- Driver info section\n\nLet me spawn the senior-frontend agent to implement this.","thinkingSignature":"65392a53d86614495e3ec669b72e51fe3e7803eec2e4d0675122999d3d502be2"},{"type":"text","text":"Đủ thông tin. Spawn senior-frontend agent để implement dashboard mới:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wi9vjtwi21ne_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are a senior frontend developer agent. Your task is to IMPLEMENT a new dashboard design for a CMS Driving Training (CMS Đào tạo lái xe) application.\n\n## Workspace\nProject root: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/`\nCurrent branch: `feat/cms-driving-training-design` (ALREADY checked out, DO NOT change branch)\nTech stack: React + Vite + Ant Design + Redux + React Router v6\n\n## Design Reference (from screenshot analysis)\nThe new dashboard should have this layout:\n\n### Header (top bar)\n- Logo area on left: \"Đào tạo lái xe\" text or image\n- Right side: notification bell icon, user avatar \"NV\" with dropdown\n- Background: white with subtle bottom border\n\n### Sidebar (left nav)\n- Logo at top: circular \"D\" icon or \"ĐTLX\" text\n- Navigation items with icons:\n  - 🏠 Trang chủ (Dashboard)\n  - 👨‍🎓 Quản lý Học viên\n  - 📅 Quản lý Lịch học / Lịch thi\n  - 🔔 Thông báo\n  - 💰 Phí & Thanh toán\n  - 📊 Báo cáo\n  - ⚙️ Cài đặt\n  - 🔒 Đăng xuất\n- Active state: highlighted background (purple/violet accent)\n- Sidebar background: white or light gray\n\n### Main Content Area\n**Section 1: Stats Row**\n- 2 large stat cards side by side:\n  - \"Giáo viên\" card: icon (👨‍🏫 or teacher icon), value \"2.000.000 ₫\", subtitle \"Tổng doanh thu\"\n  - \"Học viên\" card: icon (👨‍🎓 or student icon), value \"2.000.000 ₫\", subtitle \"Tổng doanh thu\"\n- Card style: white background, subtle shadow, rounded corners, large number in bold\n\n**Section 2: Calendar/Schedule Section**\n- Section title: \"Lịch học / Lịch thi\" with a \"+\" add button\n- View toggle: Grid icon / List icon (top right of section)\n- Grid view: 3-column grid of schedule cards (max 6 visible, rest scrollable OR pagination)\n  - Each card: Date badge (red/blue), Course name (3 lines max with ...), Time slot, Status badge\n  - \"Xem thêm\" or scroll to show more\n- List view: table format with columns: Ngày, Ca học, Khoá học, Trạng thái\n\n**Section 3: Cost Management Table (Chi phí)**\n- Section title: \"Thông kê chi phí\"\n- Horizontal scrollable table:\n  - Columns: Ngày (date), Loại chi phí (type), Số tiền (amount), Ghi chú (notes)\n  - Alternating row colors\n  - Horizontal scroll bar at bottom of table\n\n**Section 4: Driver Info (Thông tin tài xế)**\n- Cards showing driver information: Name, license type, contact info\n\n### Color Scheme\n- Primary accent: purple/violet (#8B5CF6 or similar)\n- White backgrounds for cards\n- Light gray for page background\n- Red/Orange for important stats\n\n## Implementation Steps\n\n1. First, READ and understand the existing:\n   - `src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx` - main layout\n   - `src/components/SideNav.jsx` - sidebar component  \n   - `src/pages/dashboard/chart/index.jsx` - current dashboard chart area\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/chart/card/ListCard.jsx` - current stat cards\n\n2. Create the new dashboard page. The new dashboard should REPLACE the existing ChartsDashboard component content (keep the date/agent filters and ListCard from current dashboard but redesign them).\n\n3. Key components to create:\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/StatsRow.jsx` - The 2 stat cards row (Giáo viên + Học viên)\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/CalendarSection.jsx` - Calendar grid with view toggle\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/CostTable.jsx` - Chi phí scrollable table\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/DriverInfo.jsx` - Driver info cards\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/NewSideNav.jsx` - NEW sidebar matching the design\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/chart/card/ListCard.jsx` - REDESIGN stat cards\n\n4. Update `src/pages/dashboard/chart/index.jsx` to use new components (keep the existing filters at top)\n\n5. For the calendar schedule data, use mock/placeholder data initially since the API may not be connected yet:\n   ```js\n   const mockSchedules = [\n     { id: 1, date: \"2026-04-20\", time: \"08:00 - 10:00\", course: \"Khoá A1 - Nền tảng\", status: \"Đã đăng ký\", instructor: \"Nguyễn Văn A\" },\n     { id: 2, date: \"2026-04-20\", time: \"14:00 - 16:00\", course: \"Khoá B2 - Nâng cao\", status: \"Chờ xác nhận\", instructor: \"Trần Thị B\" },\n     // ... more items\n   ];\n   ```\n\n6. For cost table mock data:\n   ```js\n   const mockCosts = [\n     { id: 1, date: \"01/04/2026\", type: \"Xăng xe\", amount: \"500.000 ₫\", note: \"Đổ xăng xe Honda\" },\n     { id: 2, date: \"03/04/2026\", type: \"Sửa chữa\", amount: \"1.200.000 ₫\", note: \"Thay lốp xe\" },\n     // ... more items\n   ];\n   ```\n\n7. Make it RESPONSIVE - work on mobile (1 column), tablet (2 columns), desktop (3+ columns)\n\n8. Use Ant Design components where appropriate (Card, Table, Button, Tag, Badge, Tabs, etc.)\n\n9. After implementing, run `yarn build` or `npm run build` to verify there are no errors.\n\n10. Commit your changes with message: \"feat(dashboard): implement CMS Driving Training dashboard design\"\n\n## Important\n- Work in the `feat/cms-driving-training-design` branch (already checked out)\n- Keep existing functionality (filters, redux) working\n- The new design should feel modern, clean, and professional\n- Do NOT install new packages unless absolutely necessary\n- When done, respond with a summary of what was implemented and any notes\n\n## Output format\nWhen complete, provide:\n1. List of files created/modified\n2. Key design decisions made\n3. Any issues encountered\n4. Commands to verify/build","label":"dtlx:dashboard-implementation","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"senior-frontend","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"mode":"run","cleanup":"keep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":580,"output":1794,"cacheRead":141982,"cacheWrite":669,"totalTokens":145025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776646505679,"responseId":"0634ac6b3feab44cbad559a74273e24c"}}
