{"type":"message","id":"787a2933","parentId":"984e6f69","timestamp":"2026-04-20T01:50:22.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's an OLD backend process running at pid 518490 (node server/server.ts) from April 19. And a newer one at pid 528506. There are TWO backend processes running! The old one might be listening on port 5555 already.\n\nBut wait - both processes might be fighting over port 5555. And the curl responded OK so something is listening.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n- PID 518490: `node server/server.ts` - OLD backend, running since Apr19\n- PID 528506: `/usr/bin/node -r ts-node/register -r tsconfig-paths/register src/server.ts` - NEW backend from today\n\n\nThe new one is running via ts-node, and both are trying to listen on the same port. Since the ss output only shows one entry, they must be on different interfaces—likely the old one bound to localhost and the new one to all interfaces. The 511 connections on the new one suggests it picked up successfully while the old one probably failed. Both started at roughly the same time, so there's likely a conflict happening.\n\nThe real issue is probably the Vite dev server proxy—if it's not configured, the frontend can't reach the backend at all. Let me check if the proxy is set up, and also verify whether port 5555 is actually reachable from outside since it's a non-standard port that some firewalls block. I'll restart the backend with explicit host binding and set up Vite to proxy the API requests instead of relying on direct external access.","thinkingSignature":"907c7b5445440cf77222a8a0b398d726b2fcb61d3b018af91ebfe45143430e8a"},{"type":"text","text":"Hai backend process đang chạy cùng lúc — có thể xung đột. Restart sạch và setup Vite proxy:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ezv6v9a47wjz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"kill 518490 528506 528444 528457 528505 2>/dev/null; sleep 2 && echo \"Killed all backend processes\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":408,"output":397,"cacheRead":157832,"cacheWrite":582,"totalTokens":159219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776649809489,"responseId":"0634b9522b0f9c1111aace2a720a54d7"}}
