{"type":"message","id":"4b806046","parentId":"2218982d","timestamp":"2026-04-20T02:09:53.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The fallback is `localhost:5000` and `VITE_API_SERVER` is now empty. The issue is the browser cached the old bundle with `localhost:5000`. I need to:\n\n1. Fix the fallback to `localhost:5555` (the actual backend port)\n2. Clear Vite cache\n3. Also need to check `auth.api.js` specifically\n\nBut actually, the real issue is that the browser is still loading the OLD cached JS from Vite's previous build that had `localhost:5000`. The new `.env` with empty `VITE_API_SERVER` will use the fallback `localhost:5000`, which is wrong.","thinkingSignature":"16f572ed5b77a4cc11a0656686c05f578e9148ae9a032992ff926c550ad37e33"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s5as5g657j1y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend && cat src/apis/auth.api.js | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":108,"output":198,"cacheRead":169410,"cacheWrite":2686,"totalTokens":172402,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776650984767,"responseId":"0634bdea1fd68e1f272a2b5d297e382f"}}
