{"type":"message","id":"defc83ee","parentId":"fef48099","timestamp":"2026-04-20T02:10:01.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the auth.api.js just imports from axiosInterceptor, which uses `VITE_API_SERVER`. The problem is:\n1. Browser caches the old bundle with `localhost:5000` \n2. Even with new `.env`, the cached JS still has the old URL\n\nLet me fix both:\n1. Fix the fallback in axiosInterceptor to be empty (use relative URL through proxy)\n2. Clear the browser cache or force a hard reload\n3. Restart the frontend dev server to ensure the new build is used\n\nActually, the simplest fix is: change the fallback in axiosInterceptor.js to `\"\"` (empty string) so it uses relative URLs that go through the Vite proxy. And update the .env to ensure VITE_API_SERVER is empty.","thinkingSignature":"329bae7b2a7926b7684660a13742d7482d05f6f35810be8897fab68936f8200d"},{"type":"text","text":"Fix fallback và xóa Vite cache:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w3vyu0j0a2v7_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/src/configs/axiosInterceptor.js","edits":[{"oldText":"const API_SERVER = import.meta.env.VITE_API_SERVER || \"http://localhost:5000\";","newText":"const API_SERVER = import.meta.env.VITE_API_SERVER || \"\";"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":159,"output":275,"cacheRead":171842,"cacheWrite":498,"totalTokens":172774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776650993246,"responseId":"0634bdf298024522f52240d624a87629"}}
