{"type":"message","id":"f571d9a0","parentId":"133e446c","timestamp":"2026-04-20T02:11:56.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! The request is now going through the Vite proxy to `http://103.253.21.139:3002/api/v1/auth/signin` (not localhost:5000 anymore). But it's getting a 404. The issue is the Vite proxy can't reach the backend.\n\nWait - the curl test showed the backend responding via the proxy. But the browser gets 404? This could be:\n1. The backend is down again\n2. The proxy path is wrong - maybe the proxy needs to be configured differently\n\nLet me check if the backend is still running and if the proxy path is correct.\n\nActually, looking at the curl results from before:\n```\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/auth/signin -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"username\":\"admin\",\"password\":\"admin\"}'\n\n\n```\n\nreturned the validation error response from backend. So the proxy works via curl. But the browser gets 404...\n\nMaybe the issue is that the backend process died. Let me check.\n\nWait, actually looking more carefully at the curl results - when I tested the curl with localhost:3002 and the right password, it returned validation error. So the proxy IS working. But now the browser gets 404... Maybe the backend died? Let me check.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"62ab19d62f313bcc70ffe184a1e72bbfcd8100c560052808505db761f6c8d432"},{"type":"text","text":"\nProxy đang hoạt động (backend responds) nhưng browser nhận 404 — backend có thể đã chết:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m059wli9w9c7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep 5555 && curl -s http://localhost:5555/ping"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":759,"output":348,"cacheRead":173326,"cacheWrite":69,"totalTokens":174502,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776651102066,"