{"type":"message","id":"536230ff","parentId":"dddfd7e8","timestamp":"2026-04-20T02:16:00.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"File doesn't exist, create it.","thinkingSignature":"03827f88bb6472808c73956c1ddd22e620d6b03875d62f954a98f00d710b6cd0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ascymq89jrk5_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-20.md","content":"# 2026-04-20 — AHV DTLX Ecosystem Session\n\n## Session Reset + Agent Bootstrap (Khương Nịnh)\n\n### Actions Taken\n- Deleted 10 old DTLX subagent sessions (DTLX project only, kept MAIY Hub + QLHV)\n- Spawned all 36 agents in DTLX ecosystem (batched, gateway unstable → many timeouts)\n- 12 agents confirmed READY: senior-frontend, senior-backend, senior-architect (Soren), senior-devops, senior-qa, prompt-optimizer, code-reviewer, security-reviewer (Shield), senior-security (Vigil), playwright-pro, shadcn-expert, content-strategy\n\n### Figma Integration\n- Figma MCP connected successfully for file `8KT67HAydXovvz3NB5GzgS` (\"Untitled\" — CMS Driving Training)\n- Comments read: logo→home, calendar→popup, text overflow (8px, max 3 lines), max 6 calendars visible with scroll/list toggle, scrollable table\n- Thumbnail images extracted for nodes 26:2326, 26:4338, 26:3059\n- File content / get_file still rate-limited; comments only\n\n### CMS Driving Training Dashboard\n- Frontend repo: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/`\n- Backend repo: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/`\n- New branch: `feat/cms-driving-training-design` (created from develop)\n- Components created: StatsRow.jsx, CalendarSection.jsx, CostTable.jsx, DriverInfo.jsx\n- Dashboard chart/index.jsx updated\n- Frontend: Vite + React + Ant Design + Redux\n- Backend: Express + TypeORM + MongoDB\n\n### Infrastructure Setup\n- Frontend dev server: port 3002 → http://103.253.21.139:3002\n- Backend: port 5555 → http://103.253.21.139:5555\n- MongoDB: port 27017 (Docker, image mongo:7)\n- Vite proxy configured: `/api` → `http://localhost:5555`\n- Frontend .env: VITE_PORT=3002, VITE_API_SERVER= (empty → relative URLs via proxy)\n- Backend CORS fixed: changed `origin: '*'` → `origin: ['http://localhost:3000', 'http://103.253.21.139:3002', 'http://localhost:3002']`\n\n### Auth Status\n- Backend API responding correctly\n- Login returns HTTP 404 (wrong password) — not a real error, credentials not confirmed\n- Credentials unknown — need to check MongoDB for default admin user\n\n### Pending\n- Agent implementation for new dashboard design — still in progress (agent v2 spawned)\n- Default admin credentials for DTLX backend — need to check MongoDB\n- Vite proxy working but needs restart on .env change\n- Figma file content still rate-limited; using comments + image nodes as context\n\n## GitLab Repos\n- Frontend: `gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend` (branch `feat/cms-driving-training-design`)\n- Backend: `gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend` (branch `feat/cms-driving-training-design`)\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":76,"output":800,"cacheRead":48131,"cacheWrite":509,"totalTokens":49516,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776651344293,"responseId":"0634bf517db34d4f94f2c25db5089959"}}
